task.summary: Bug fix. Always set SmartPlug id XML-Attribute to "edimax" rather than the name assigned to the plug., Dependency update, Added basic Travis builds
Added missing commit from previous release
Dependency updates, Replaced deprecated use of Promise.settle(), Minor changes of demo.js
Dependency updates, Replaced lodash with lightweight lodash method modules
Added device discovery service, Replaced lodash with lightweight lodash method modules
Fix: ensure discovery service will timeout if no results received
Bug fix: Close discovery socket on error, Improved error handling
Dependency updates, updated Travis build descriptor
Added functions to get the current schedule state (cherry picked from commit bee5113)
Updated list of contributors, dependency updates
support for digest authentication required with firmware versions SP-2101W v2.08 and SP-1101W v2.04
updated and revised dependencies. Now using Object.assign instead of lodash assign
use util.inspect instead of JSON.stringify to avoid circular dependencies error if debugging is enabled, use Object.assign instead of lodash assign
